Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:18.58,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,350)}揮灑汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:22.87,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,350)}飽餐一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:30.49,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,350)}好好睡一覺  放鬆全身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:35.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,350)}無邪歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:39.87,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,350)}盡情哭泣
